4 SECTION 2. EXTRA HELP - UTILITIES DIVISION. There is hereby
5 authorized, for the Arkansas Public Service Commission - Utilities Division
6 for the 2025-2026 fiscal year, the following maximum number of part-time or
7 temporary employees, to be known as "Extra Help", payable from funds
8 appropriated herein for such purposes: six (6) temporary or part-time
9 employees, when needed, at rates of pay not to exceed those provided in the
10 Uniform Classification and Compensation Act, or its successor, or this act
11 for the appropriate classification.
12
