14 appropriated, to the Arkansas Public Service Commission, to be payable from
15 the Public Service Commission Fund, for personal services and operating
16 expenses of the Arkansas Public Service Commission - Utilities Division for
17 the fiscal year ending June 30, 2026, the following:
